      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It requires significant mechanical attention, as the engine is currently running roughly and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. The exterior has multiple dents, faded paint, and some rust spots, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear on the upholstery. This would be an ideal candidate for a dedicated mechanic or someone looking for a parts car, but it is not currently in road-ready condition.",
