      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go. It is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it spotless and staying on top of every single service. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 43900.0,
