      "description": "This is, quite simply, a time capsule on wheels. Every inch of this vehicle has been meticulously preserved to maintain its showroom-fresh appearance. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirls, rock chips, or imperfections. Inside, the premium leather upholstery looks and smells brand new, with absolutely zero bolster wear or creasing. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control,",
